{"tid":1890293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新冠肺炎患者死亡過程痛苦 前綫醫生：如同浸死","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T06:24:41.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fcebbbe8fb6a8d01565ab6105c52e8c65d0410a","tid":1890293,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200220/_2020022010094618044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200220%2F_2020022010094618044.jpg&h=026c8237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，內地確診個案超過7萬多宗，逾2000人死亡。微博日前驚傳一則題為「一線的醫生的話」的文章，指新冠肺炎死亡感受很痛苦，「跟淹死一樣。」內容令人不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n文章詳細描述新冠肺炎患者的「死前感受」，「一直呼吸困難，直到最後幾分鐘，病人全程清醒，病人會呼救，會哭著喊著說醫生你救救我&hellip;&hellip;，伴隨著劇烈地掙扎，直到呼出最後一口氣。」文章又指，新冠肺炎死因本質上和淹死一樣，由於大量水進入肺部，氧氣不能進入，「肺被病毒導致的果凍狀的分泌物給佔滿了，換氣功能完全喪失，再濃的氧也進不去血裡面；而吸痰也沒用，因為靠氣管鏡到達不了那個終末端的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n文章還提到，治療新冠肺炎患者沒有特效藥，「只能把純氧輸送給病人，不經口插管，維持大概三至五天後，如果他的血氧飽和度能上升到正常範圍，他也就挺過了呼吸衰竭這一關，但如果挺不過，就可能要切開氣管，或插管等醫療行為。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，他提到「國家派了幾萬醫護人員去武漢，說明這個病不好治。現在所有的治療，都是安慰性的治療。」這段說話讓人絕望。<br />\n<br />\n其實，內地傳染病專家鍾南山日前曾透露了新冠肺炎病患的屍檢細節。他說，新冠肺炎患者肺的表現和SARS有點不一樣，「沒有嚴重纖維化，現在還沒有結果，看起來有一部分肺泡還存在，但是炎症很厲害，有大量非常黏的黏液，這將導致病人的通氣不通順。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1205225/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6-%E5%89%8D%E7%B6%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%A6%82%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1205225%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E7%2597%259B%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=7c90ffeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1205225%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E7%2597%259B%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E6%25AD%25BB&h=52779da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1205225/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6-%E5%89%8D%E7%B6%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%A6%82%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E6%AD%BB</a>"},{"pid":"4a0dc52aebc178321c10cbafe75bbb4c57c48e61","tid":1890293,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n21/2 【Twitter 要人】美國議員繼續全方位追擊中共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890257</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求入去幫推加 <span style=\"color: gold;\">rt + like + reply</span>"},{"pid":"adc08fb1343f5323449c7db8fdd0ea3f59e89703","tid":1890293,"uid":195821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"我幫鍾南山講埋：未來14天是關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105a6ce049230fd9b75493cf13896a0bc2db1ec5","tid":1890293,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"adc08fb1343f5323449c7db8fdd0ea3f